    {
      "id": 5,
      "name": "孟桂英",
      "color": "#c379f2",
      "content": "人类还真是脆弱的生物，我最讨厌脆弱的东西。明明就很脆弱还去帮人，明明就没有能力还要拼命的去保护谁。",
      "time": "5小时前",
      "imgs": [
        "assets/images/discover/friends/wx_img9.JPG",
        "assets/images/discover/friends/wx_img10.JPG",
        "assets/images/discover/friends/wx_img11.JPG"
